OL,3,CGM hospital trusts pay out almost #6
OL,4,Cmillion for injuries to mums and babies
OL,6,FThree hospital trusts in Greater
OL,7,FManchester have paid out almost #6
OL,8,Fmillion in compensation for injuries
OL,9,Fsuffered by mothers and babies during
OL,10,Fbirth in the last two years. One
OL,11,FGreater Manchester hospital trust paid
OL,12,Fout #3.8 million in birth injury
OL,13,Fcompensation in the past two years
OL,14,Falone - while another trust has also
OL,15,Fpaid more than a million in damages in
OL,16,Fthe same timeframe.
