OL,6,FTameside and Glossop Integrated Care
OL,7,FNHS Foundation Trust, which runs
OL,8,FTameside Hospital, has paid out
OL,9,F#3,802,500 in compensation for birth
OL,10,Finjury claims from November 2021 to
OL,11,FNovember 2023, data from a Freedom of
OL,12,FInformation request (FOI) seen by the
OL,13,FM.E.N has shown. The birth injury rate
OL,14,Fat the trust during that period was
OL,15,F394 injuries per 1,000 deliveries.
