OL,6,FData also revealed that a total of 149
OL,7,Fperineal (vaginal) tears were suffered
OL,8,Fby mothers following childbirth at the
OL,9,Ftrust. Of those, 58 were first degree,
OL,10,F81 were second degree and 10 were
OL,11,Fthird degree tears. Around 30 women
OL,12,Fsuffered pelvic fractures, including
OL,13,Ffractures to the public bone, coccyx
OL,14,For sacrum.
