OL,6,FThe data follows the launch of the
OL,7,Ffirst-ever UK parliamentary committee
OL,8,Finto birth trauma this year, amid
OL,9,Fclaims of 'shockingly poor care' being
OL,10,Fcommon in the NHS.
OL,12,FConservative MP, Theo Clarke is co-
OL,13,Fchair of the cross-parliamentary
OL,14,Fcommittee alongside Labour MP, Rosie
OL,15,FDuffield. The first hearing is set for
OL,16,FFebruary 5, with findings due to be
OL,17,Fpublished in April.
