OL,6,FIn the House of Commons last week, Ms
OL,7,FClarke spoke of how the issue of birth
OL,8,Ftrauma is 'a real taboo'. The MP
OL,9,Frecounted her own birthing horror
OL,10,Fafter having to undergo emergency
OL,11,Fsurgery for a serious third degree
OL,12,Ftear while giving birth to her
OL,13,Fdaughter after a 40-hour labour.
