OL,6,FThe Birth Trauma Association is a
OL,7,Fsupporter and contributor to the
OL,8,Fcommittee and says there have been
OL,9,Fmany tales of 'shockingly poor care'
OL,10,Fwithin maternity units of the NHS. The
OL,11,Fassociation's CEO, Kim Thomas, said:
OL,12,F"We know from what women tell us that
OL,13,Fexperiences of shockingly poor care
OL,14,Fare also common in the NHS.
OL,16,F"But these women find that they are
OL,17,Frarely listened to ` often complaints
OL,18,Fto hospitals are met with attempts to
OL,19,Fminimise the woman's trauma and deny
OL,20,Fresponsibility."
