OL,6,FAccording to NHS Resolution,
OL,7,F'maternity claims represent the
OL,8,Fhighest value and second highest
OL,9,Fnumber of clinical negligence claims'.
OL,10,FBirth injuries are often traumatic,
OL,11,Frequiring mothers to undergo emergency
OL,12,Fsurgeries and long-term recovery all
OL,13,Fwhile caring for a newborn.
