OL,6,F"At the moment, a lot of birth
OL,7,Finjuries go undiagnosed, causing
OL,8,Fserious problems," says Ms Thomas. A
OL,9,Fthird or fourth degree tear, also
OL,10,Fknown as an anal sphincter tear, can
OL,11,Fbe repaired if diagnosed early enough,
OL,12,Fbut if left untreated, it can leave
OL,13,Fwomen with lifelong faecal
OL,14,Fincontinence, which can be very
OL,15,Fdistressing."
