OL,6,FShe added: "At the Birth Trauma
OL,7,FAssociation, we hear a lot of stories
OL,8,Fof birth injuries caused by medical
OL,9,Fnegligence. However, many women never
OL,10,Freceive compensation for these
OL,11,Finjuries. Contrary to public
OL,12,Fperception, suing the NHS can be very
OL,13,Fhard."
